#: rulesets/classic.desktop:2 themes/classic.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Classic"
msgstr "Klasično"

# well-spelled: брзобота
#: rulesets/classic.desktop:66
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<qt><p>The rules used in the original BSD command line version of "
"<tt>robots</tt>.</p><p>Nothing fancy, just the basic game elements: no "
"fastbots, no safe teleports, no pushing junkheaps, and a huge game grid.</"
"p><p>Due to its larger width, it is recommended that you use a theme with "
"narrower tiles to better fit your screen.</p></qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt><p>Skup pravila iz originalne BSD komandnolinijske verzije <tt>robots</"
"tt>. Ništa nalickano, samo osnovni elementi igre: bez brzobota, bezbednih "
"teleportovanja ili guranja krševa, i ogromno igračko polje.</p><p>Zbog "
"velike širine, preporučljivo je izabrati temu sa užim pločicama kako bi "
"bolje stalo na ekran.</p></qt>"

#: rulesets/daleks.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Daleks"
msgstr "Daleci"

#: rulesets/daleks.desktop:52
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<qt><p>An approximation of the rules used in Daleks, a robots-like game for "
"early Apple computers.</p><p>The hero is allotted one energy each round that "
"can be used to power the sonic screwdriver. All other special features are "
"disabled.</p></qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt><p>Pravila slična onima iz Daleka, robotolike igre za rane Appleove "
"računare.</p><p>Junak dobija po jedinicu energije u svakoj rundi, koja služi "
"kao napajanje zvučnog šrafcigera. Sve druge posebne mogućnosti su isključene."
"</p></qt>"

#: rulesets/default.desktop:2 src/org.kde.killbots.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Killbots"
msgstr "K‑zloboti"

#: rulesets/default.desktop:58
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<qt><p>The default Killbots game type.</p><p>Includes a medium size grid, "
"safe teleports, fast enemies and pushable junkheaps.</p></qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt><p>Podrazumevani tip igre K‑zlobota.</p><p>Uključuje srednje veliko "
"polje, bezbedno teleportovanje, brze neprijatelje i krševe koji se mogu "
"gurati.</p></qt>"

#: rulesets/easy.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Easy"
msgstr "Lako"

#: rulesets/easy.desktop:58
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<qt><p>An easier version of the \"Killbots\" game type.</p><p>Includes a "
"bigger game grid prepopulated with junkheaps, a starting stash of energy and "
"an increasing energy cap.</p></qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt><p>Lakša verzija igre K‑zloboti.</p><p>Uključuje veće igračko polje već "
"prošarano krševima, početnom zalihom energije i povećavajućim ograničenjem "
"energije.</p></qt>"

#: rulesets/energycrisis.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Energy Crisis"
msgstr "Energetska kriza"

#: rulesets/energycrisis.desktop:52
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"The player starts with 30 energy and cannot earn more. How many rounds can "
"you survive and how many points can you collect before your energy and luck "
"run out?"
msgstr ""
"Igrač počinje sa energijom 30 i ne može zaraditi još. Koliko rundi možete "
"preživeti i koliko poena možete sakupiti pre nego što vas energija i sreća "
"napuste?"

#: src/org.kde.killbots.desktop:56
msgctxt "GenericName"
msgid "Strategy Game with Robots"
msgstr "Strateška igra sa robotima"

#: src/org.kde.killbots.desktop:97
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "A KDE game of killer robots and teleportation."
msgstr "KDE‑ova igra robota ubica i teleportacije"

#: themes/classic.desktop:64
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "A theme for those who miss the console version"
msgstr "Tema za one kojima nedostaje konzolna verzija"

#: themes/mountainadventure.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Mountain Adventure"
msgstr "Planinska avantura"

# well-spelled: Гномс
#: themes/mountainadventure.desktop:52
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "Indiana Gnomes battles ghosts and bats on a misty mountainside."
msgstr ""
"Indijana Gnoms bori se protiv duhova i šišmiša na maglovitom proplanku."

#: themes/mummymadness.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Mummy Madness"
msgstr "Ludilo s mumijama"

#: themes/mummymadness.desktop:50
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "Egyptian style theme with mad mummies."
msgstr "Tema u egipatskom stilu, sa ludim mumijama"

#: themes/robotkill.desktop:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Robot Kill"
msgstr "Ubij robota"

#: themes/robotkill.desktop:52
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "The default Killbots theme."
msgstr "Podrazumevana tema K‑zlobota."
